{"tid":1941893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 推到全港舖頭都睇到！！］所有人入舖頭前都要CHECK手帶！","createTime":"2020-03-24T17:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T02:17:00.000Z","uid":249923,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82b8e3c9531a9225083b3e157ff9defaae4e0a11","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"每個人入舖頭前都要經職員check下有冇帶住手帶，confirm冇帶先比入<br />\n<br />\n唔肯比人check既人，唔比佢入舖頭，跟手打去舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇你班自私撚去得邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正好多舖頭入去之前都要量體溫，唔爭在check埋有冇手帶啦"},{"pid":"9322c6aaab4e1bc93caa47d7a99d0223f99cce46","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6565100639febe94f3753fd4bc1850a5b4e836a2","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"df6044614ff15a2da9f654053cdd9d39eddc7c1e","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"2ae8e75f442d4f65f3a34e594c7fce2806e23a5b","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"推4！"},{"pid":"29f1b0121f8a6d9d42503e26f6847e27c7261f09","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"c4a0eb5e6868913bdc2235e6f1bba9cd2abd1bec","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:10:25.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"ba04da5c2488c1722156fadbd194399eb6a90e55","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"f00627c6f14b78b77414ed23db5e8ea0e3ed44f3","tid":1941893,"uid":249923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:11:4